<p><strong>Broadsword</strong>&nbsp;is a <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Straight Swords" href="/Straight+Swords" target="">Straight Sword</a>&nbsp;in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Wiki" href="/Elden+Ring+Wiki">Elden Ring</a>. The <strong>Broadsword</strong>&nbsp;scales primarily with <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Strength" href="/Strength" target="">Strength</a>&nbsp;and <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Dexterity" href="/Dexterity" target="">Dexterity</a>&nbsp;and is a good <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Weapons" href="/Weapons" target="">Weapon</a> for melee combat, and dealing slashing attacks to enemies.&nbsp;</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<div class="lineleft"> 
 <p><em>A straight sword with a wide blade, suited to slashing attacks.</em></p> 
 <p><em>Horizontal swings boast wide attack range, making it easier to connect with foes.&nbsp;</em></p> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Where to Find Broadsword in&nbsp;Elden Ring</h3> 
<p>The Broadsword weapon can be found at the following locations:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Starting Equipment for the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Confessor" href="/Confessor" target="">Confessor</a> Class</li> 
 <li>Can be bought from the&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Nomadic Merchant West Limgrave" href="/Nomadic+Merchant+West+Limgrave">Nomadic Merchant</a>&nbsp;for&nbsp;<img title="runes-currency-elden-ring-wiki-guide-18" src="/file/Elden-Ring/runes-currency-elden-ring-wiki-guide-18.png" alt="runes currency elden ring wiki guide 18" width="18" height="18">&nbsp;1800&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Runes" href="/Runes" target="">Runes</a>. He is located south-east of&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Coastal Cave" href="/Coastal+Cave" target="">Coastal Cave</a>. [<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=6&amp;lat=-196.5&amp;lng=97.660389&amp;zoom=8" href="/Interactive+Map?id=6&amp;lat=-196.5&amp;lng=97.660389&amp;zoom=8">Map Link</a>]</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Elden Ring Broadsword Notes &amp; Tips</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Weapon <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Skills" href="/Skills" target="">Skill</a>: <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Square Off" href="/Square+Off" target="">Square Off</a></li> 
 <li>This weapon can be infused with&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Ashes of War" href="/Ashes+of+War" target="">Ashes of War</a>&nbsp;and buffed with&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Magic" href="/Magic" target="">Magic</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Consumables" href="/Consumables" target="">Consumables</a>.</li> 
 <li><strong>Broadsword</strong> can be upgraded by using <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Smithing Stones" href="/Smithing+Stones" target="">Smithing Stones</a>.</li> 
 <li>Sell Value:&nbsp;&nbsp;<img title="Runes" src="/file/Elden-Ring/er-runes-13.png" alt="er runes 13" width="18" height="18">&nbsp;100 <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Runes" href="/Runes">Runes</a></li> 
</ul> 
<p>The Broadsword can be infused with <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Ashes of War" href="/Ashes+of+War" target="">Ashes of War</a>. Click below for a list of all possible Ashes of War that can be applied to the straight sword.</p> 
